ex (roughly speaking a new kind of uncertainty principle).\nBoth of these arise from a significant majorization result. This work\ncomplements recent studies in quantum computation where the deviation of the\nBorn Rule from the LTP is measured in terms of negativity of Wigner functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 16:27:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 16:35:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 19:55:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-04"}
