 appreciably shorter than in the prograde case. We\nalso provide the smoothing length required in 2D simulations in order to\naccount for 3D effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 20:32:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
