ons trapped in a 2D\npotential is considered. It is demonstrated that they may form a slowly\nrotating robust \\textquotedblleft molecule\", if aninitial kicks are applied to\nthem in opposite directions, perpendicular to the line connecting their\ncenters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 May 2018 13:49:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
